      <title>赛百味以 23.4 亿美元交易增加特许经营支持债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/subway-grows-franchise-backed-debt-pile-in-2-34-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赛百味已出售价值 23.4 亿美元的证券，这是这家三明治连锁店在短短三个月内进行的第二笔以特许经营权等资产为支撑的交易，该公司在美国可能降息之前对收购债务进行了再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/subway-grows-franchise-backed-debt-pile-in-2-34-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:59:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登助手正在制定美国主权财富基金提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/biden-aides-working-on-proposal-for-us-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登的高级助手一直在起草一项提案，旨在创建一个主权财富基金，允许美国投资国家安全利益，包括技术、能源和供应链中的关键环节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/biden-aides-working-on-proposal-for-us-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
